## Next Steps
*   Further research into the "deployment risk" of interoperable E2EE to provide better watchdogging of platform implementations.
*   Continued coordination with the MIMI (More Instant Messaging Interoperability) working group regarding identity and trust models.
*   Ongoing work on integrating MLS into decentralized social protocols like ActivityPub.